<!-- ++++++++++++++++++ discrete_shield ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Discrete_shield_mim.discrete_shield">
<p>
A <b>discrete_shield</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_design_view:mim:Physical_unit_design_view_mim.physical_component"/> that implements the ARM concept of
 <express_ref linkend="Discrete_shield:arm:Discrete_shield_arm.Physical_shield"/>, when the shield is comprised of a component or
components that are manufactured separately from the interconnect component.  
</p></ext_description>

<!-- +++ WR: discrete_shield.WR1 +++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Discrete_shield_mim.discrete_shield.wr:WR1">
The <b>discrete_shield</b> shall have a <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition.frame_of_reference"/> name of 'physical
occurrence'.
</ext_description>

<!-- +++ WR: discrete_shield.WR2 +++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Discrete_shield_mim.discrete_shield.wr:WR2">
The <b>discrete_shield</b> shall be related to at least one  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_design_view:mim:Physical_unit_design_view_mim.component_definition"/> or
at least one  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_design_view:mim:Physical_unit_design_view_mim.component_definition"/> as the 'shielded item'.
</ext_description>


